Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs43\bord0\fad(417,458)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\pos(640,540)}2039年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs43\bord0\shad0\fad(417,458)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\pos(640,538)}联合国军最终决战舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs43\bord0\shad0\fad(417,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\pos(640,510)}“海雾”大型舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军目标健在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的攻击都失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类剩下的所有战力都集中到这场战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此的数量依然无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21世纪初
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类由于全球变暖等影响 失去了地上的绝大多数版图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就像在呼应这一情况一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相不明的“海雾”大战舰群出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封锁了所有运输航道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类从所有的海洋中被驱赶了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HEFE9E1&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(332,588)}分散式首都 东京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最终决战后的7年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政治与经济纷纷崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通信卫星和海底电缆也被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:02:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且由于它们释放的电磁干扰 所有的通信都被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各国均无奈地处于孤立状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连互相是否存在也无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(404,588)}佐贺县航天发射中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把状况显示到荧幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的“海雾”…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗅探到里面的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我挡住它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到发射的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点准备发射SSTO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.22,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\an7\bord1}SSTO（Single-Stage to Orbit）：可在宇宙空间飞行，能多次使用的超音速运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,540)}“海雾”舰队 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,702)}轻巡洋舰长良
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(544,588)}航天发射中心飞弹防御系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天津风号与太刀风号沉没！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“海雾”即将脱离水雷区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就没有什么对策了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所属不明的潜艇正迅速接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的增援吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个讯号特征…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 伊号401！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HE7E7E7&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,597)}“海雾”潜艇 I-401
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们接受的委托内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止“海雾”的前进 亦或是将其击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到SSTO发射成功为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜 报告数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长良级轻巡洋舰 长良
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排水量6010吨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装备有强制波动装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12.3cm口径连装炮塔3座6门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰底部装备有鱼雷发射管12门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外还拥有雷射高射炮3门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有飞弹发射模块 近迫武器系统等多数武装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大速度60节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有潜水能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,标准的“海雾”轻巡洋舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杏平！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各鱼雷装填
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七号发射管 侵蚀鱼雷发射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检测到高速推进音 两枚鱼雷正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1-2号发射管 速射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭引擎 下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急速下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展开克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.08,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\an7\bord1}克莱因力场（Klein Field）：强制波动装甲产生的力场，能生成形似克莱因瓶的通道偏转能量\N所以称为克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距鱼雷击中还有 5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀型鱼雷即将命中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-2\an8}2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-2\an8}1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长良 转向右舷 同时展开克莱因力场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊号401… 苍蓝钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\bord1\blur2\shad0\c&HFFFCFF&\3c&H3D3836&\pos(647,499)}航路所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大陆间联络用SSTO发射成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼 哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在日本难道还有东西可以送去外国吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有才发射的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长良 你只是服从命令罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为使用克莱因力场有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“海雾”是为什么出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是为了什么而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是单纯的为了服从命令而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为我的命令才战斗着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是您的舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从两年前醒来的那时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(960,589)}2年前 横须贺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\bord1\shad0\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(915,594)}海洋技术综合学院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早群像这次也被选入了视察小组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr5\fs30\pos(573.6,20.8)}公告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(583.467,151.466)}下列人员请在指定的时间前往指定的地点报道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(476.496,222.78)}日期: 9月14日  14:00～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(502.782,268.494)}地点: 干部候补生校舍201讲堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr7\fs20\pos(479.011,308.265)}人员名单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.41,text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr5\fs20\pos(698.744,629.598)}海洋技术学院 校长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为成绩很优秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该不止这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早是牺牲的舰长大人的独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们不同 他是被优待的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到那个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的父亲投奔“海雾”的谣传是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海战的情报又没公开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 千早总有些黑幕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你们看到的东西将是最重要军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只被许可对你们这些将来受期待的学生公开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要机密…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晚会成为士官的你们有知道的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是组织上传达事项罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\c&HDEDEDE&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(980,595)}第51号仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜水艇 伊号401…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是被捕获的“海雾”的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外观虽是模仿太平洋战争的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却不是人造之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面居然还藏着这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实 这不是能公开的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大海战后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这艘潜水艇锁定了武装出现在了这个港口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其理由目的均未知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙毫无抵抗被我们捕获了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能解明这艘船的原理的话 说不定“海雾”的弱点也能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们已经研究了7年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经把能想到的手段全部尝试了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还是不让我们进入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说解体也做不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是十分丢脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“海雾”的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的…敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早… 群像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快收集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是 重力反应？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401 启动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关上天花板的防护壁 现在赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！ 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校有那样一个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字吖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是在找谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超级 美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有事找你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 是个美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是 千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早翔像的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“去见千早翔像的儿子”我被这样命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的恶作剧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就光想些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 这不是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么会提到我去世的父亲的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上 你一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群像 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样死脑筋的人反而被搭讪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软呼呼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类的…感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能说明把我叫出来的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确的说 是我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没时间陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离起床时间还有11个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想为没意义的事情浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 没意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接说有什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“去见千早翔像的儿子群像 并听从他的命令”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我记忆里 唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在七年间一直与外部隔离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是服从于命令…的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早群像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被吩咐要服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认：你的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拥有能打破当下这种停滞状态的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算留在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只能平静地度过毫无意义的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我活着不是为了做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于 我可以启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-401 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-401 从机密码头离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种事怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…“海雾”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一知道的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你接触 然后服从你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我记忆里 唯一的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服从命令而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们渴望着命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你成为我的船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群像…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乘上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要穿过屏障了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要反击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能承受得住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人进入我这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演算来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜航呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子稳定器初始设定还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离力场还有5秒消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱因力场消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰尾中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我现在什么都无法改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就和死没什么区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子稳定器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入待机状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401 丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 没有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被动声纳有反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.35,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs31\an7}被动声纳：也叫杂讯声纳，不发出任何讯号，只接收和处理水中目标发出的辐射杂讯或声纳讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在索敌范围内没有敌舰反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一位舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊欧娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的记忆中我是被取了这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时候开始 我们一直是逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我一起去 为了找到群像所寻求的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了“海雾”的人 蛮不错的答卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\c&HEFE9E1&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(952,595)\fad(0,400)}分散式首都 长崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord1\shad0\c&HCCC9C5&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,596)}军务省助理秘书长 上阴龙二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次SSTO的事辛苦你了 千早群像君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是委托人上阴先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能早点雇佣我的话 军队的损失就能减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于“海雾”的干扰 我们无法长距离通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这种强人所难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 大人有大人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政治吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是诡辩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是在绕道而行不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是每个人都能像你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有从事着肮脏工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 既然委托完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他出了什么事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会被“她”攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早君 你这样战斗下去会有出路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说 我对你在这两年间与“海雾”战斗的战绩有很高的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚收到消息说 SSTO被摧毁在卫星轨道上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个上面搭载有日本研究开发的最新兵器“振动弹头”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“振动弹头”？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你跟“海雾”孤军战斗的两年间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也并没有闲着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是美国？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本已经没有能够量产它们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早群像君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个工作想委托给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望你能运送它…这个人类的希望 最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新兵器是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是解析了“海雾”的侵蚀鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且改良了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为黑箱未知的部分虽然还有很多是没错 但是如果能量产的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类说不定就能迎来反击的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是美国还存在的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这么不吉利的话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事跟美国的秘密协定大概是三个月前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就停止了联络
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是什么状况也完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊欧娜 真的不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被切断了与其他船只的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能知道的就只有自己发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有海上直接运输这一条路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大陆现在十分的内乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过内陆去运送反而很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连同胞人类也无法信任什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 舰长接受了这份委托是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有我们能完成这份委托
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新武器样本的接收将在横须贺港
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航路设定为横须贺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去接收人类的希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的希望…么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆压制了I-401 不是更好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401 是有自我意识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它只服从千早群像的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心智模型吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.66,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32}心智模型（Mental Model）：“海雾”舰队伊型潜艇以及重巡洋舰以上级别才拥有的人型意志体，\N每艘都有独立意志，并可互相沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“海雾”的叛徒和人类的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分有趣的组合不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HB5C5DB&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(249.6,588)}佐渡洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\bord1\shad0\c&HD5D2CF&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,540)\fad(0,400)}“海雾”舰队 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HF0F0F0&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(640,699)\fad(0,400)}旗舰·大战舰金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长良被击沉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体也差不多习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金刚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摩耶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(805.667,535.333)}久米岛洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(1097,604)}“海雾”舰队 \N东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HDAE8FA&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(916,651)}重巡洋舰摩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401不都出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道就没有什么可以做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北面的话 是高雄的管辖范围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给那孩子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能别管什么管辖范围吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服从阿德米拉提密码的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs-3\pos(618.4,657)}Admiralty Code
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.47,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\shad0}阿德米拉提密码（Admiralty Code）：“海雾”舰队正在寻找的神秘密码，又称“失落的敕命”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金刚你这石头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(808,531)}远州洋面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(1097,604)}“海雾”舰队\N 东洋第一巡逻舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,401往这边来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord1\shad0\c&HC9C7D3&\3c&H3E3734&\pos(941.6,653.2)}重巡洋舰高雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.35,0:22:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入了人类的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我高雄将她化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}I look across a raging war and feel the steady beating of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.24,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我望向激烈的战场 感受我心脏不断的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.91,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}嵐の前の靜けさに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:53.91,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}迎着暴风雨前的寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.60,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}刃を振り下ろしていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.60,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}手起刀落斩开平淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:14.23,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}繰り返しa memory fading 今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:14.23,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}反反复复的记忆也已褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:19.27,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}時代を超えてI tell a story響く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:19.27,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}慢慢讲述超越时空的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:24.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣戦布告の詩 残酷に染もる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:24.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣战之歌已染上残酷的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}この誓いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这份誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:29.86,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}We'll fight until the bitter end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:29.86,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们要血战到底直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.10,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}途切れた息の根を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:34.10,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}将骤然停止的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.35,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}汚れた世界を繋ぎ止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:37.35,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与这污秽的世界相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.36,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}僕らの歯車を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.36,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们身上滚动的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}it's time to Stop & Rewind(Stop & Rewind)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:42.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}是时候令其倒回重来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.18,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}失った冀望を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.18,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}找回失去的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.38,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}壞れた時間のピースを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:47.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}收集破碎的时间断片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.30,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}取り戻す為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.30,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}为了去取回失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:52.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}you need to Fall & Unwind(Fall & Unwind)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:52.24,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}你只需跟从脚步放下包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.52,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}走り出す鼓動さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.52,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}充斥迈向前方的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:57.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}限りない慈しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:57.06,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与无边无际的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:59.35,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}導き出すアルペジオ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:59.35,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}演奏出美丽的琶音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:00.85,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:00.85,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}救歌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.69,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}A Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.69,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这是救歌之人
